    "title": "Walk-in Drive Logistics Manager at Blue Dart",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Blue Dart. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Logistics Manager to strengthen our Nashik-based team.\n\nAbout Blue Dart:\nBlue Dart is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in WMS\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nashik, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Blue Dart!",
